            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This is the worst school I have ever seen in my life. The management thinks teachers are not human but robots. They are forcefully asking teachers to come on Saturdays and Sundays; otherwise, they will deduct the salary. Management, are you even human? How can you think that teachers should come on weekends for the admission process? You need to hire competent people who know how to handle the admission process during weekdays. I really want a response to this review, especially from the person who made this rule for teachers to work seven days a week.",
          "publisher": {
