          "reviewBody": "Kindly do not put your ward in this school. Pls take time to scroll through all.reviews being posted at the bottom .\nThis school has hired goons to drive their buses route no 26 driver literally hit my car and ram away imagine ur little children being rash driven by a driver and I have all the proofs and videos of both the driver and the conductor. When I contacted the school the admission head Ms Reema didn't help with anything and passed on the call to Mr. Ashu the transport head who had nothing else to.say except for ma'am pls give us time we will look in to it. I mean seriously someone who is being harrassed by your driver on school duty with videos as proofs and u dont even have the audacity to look in to it on urgent basis and consider this an emergency situation. The driver scared the hell out of me clicking my pics and threatened to kill me along with the pic of my car.\nPathetic and shameful....shame on everyone here",
